":"2017-07-24T16:18:26.000Z","msg":"咩app先？<br />\n如果百度咁冇去錯，唔算係新聞啦。"},{"pid":"7214fda216469cf1855b6950bd529517c90a7f62","tid":334050,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T20:04:21.000Z","msg":"納稅人比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161c5dec37db251f4c94fa739ecd271397701369","tid":334050,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T20:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">土沉香</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗起今日另一單野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170724/large/1500830831_1a7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170724%2Flarge%2F1500830831_1a7a.jpg&h=4074fcfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【13:15更新內容】女事主報稱為內地大學生，聲稱遭賊人喝令脫衣摸胸。<br />\n<br />\n一名報稱來自湖北的23歲女大學生，昨日在落馬洲過境後，入住荃灣青山公路135號一間酒店，昨晚11時許，她報稱一名年約20歲至30歲男子敲其房門，她未有理會，其後有兩名男子假扮清潔工人進入其房間後，兩人喝令她拿出財物，之後更露出狼相，著女生脫衣，並向她摸胸非禮，兩人得逞後偕同黨逃去，女事主被劫去約2,300元現金。<br />\n<br />\n女事主其後通知保安協助報警，警員到場調查，案件列作行劫及非禮，交由荃灣警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進，通緝三名年約20至30歲本地男子。另外，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">由於女生持中國護照，屬過境性質，並不能留港居住，涉嫌逾期居留被捕。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170724/56994726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170724%2F56994726&d=QwmHDIQMkF5p0IdhLXjCG26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=bfdf0126\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170724%2F56994726&h=83b553f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170724/56994726</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2t0uq5dv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2t0uq5dv&h=8d8de9a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ybewtz0k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fybewtz0k&h=eb62f4b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b7351afee2e96264544e7f85ffb44c51a508b83","tid":334050,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T22:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f70ca3526727007f44dc21e9386d0bcb9e4f31d","tid":334050,"uid":14078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T02:25:40.000Z","msg":"先唔理果條友係大陸人定外星人<br />\n用APPLE MAP就係白痴<br />\n<br />\n利申 iPhone 7用家"}]}